+/** Undo information for a CTxIn
+ *
+ *  Contains the prevout's CTxOut being spent, and if this was the
+ *  last output of the affected transaction, its metadata as well
+ *  (coinbase or not, height, transaction version)
+ */
+class CTxInUndo
